title: Hour 1 - Browns Trade Deadline Dilemma, Burrow on His Back
itunes:title: Hour 1 - Browns Trade Deadline Dilemma, Burrow on His Back
description:
Dan considers the predicament the Cleveland Browns find themselves in as the NFL trade deadline is here and their running back Kareem Hunt is a tantalizing trade piece. And he is concerned that Joe Burrow is setting records for getting sacked in his career.
